{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "e-mall-api-collection-v2",
		"name": "E-Mall 微服务API测试集",
		"description": "电商微服务系统核心接口测试集合。覆盖用户、商品、订单、库存模块共14个核心接口，总请求27次。重点验证业务逻辑正确性、OpenFeign远程调用、Gateway路由鉴权能力。\n\n## 网关鉴权规则\n- 白名单(无需Token): /api/user/login, /api/user/register, /api/product/list, /api/product/detail\n- 受保护(需Bearer Token): /api/user/info, /api/order/**, /api/inventory/**, /api/product/add, /api/product/stock/update\n\n## Feign远程调用验证\n- 创建订单: order-service → product-service(查询商品) → inventory-service(扣减库存)\n- 取消订单: order-service → inventory-service(恢复库存)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
